deck: Once the king of the Snow Kingdom died, his realm was covered by snow. New queen, a master of dark magic, is feared by her people. Their last hope is Snow White - the rightful heir to the throne. They think she didn't survive the wrath of the tyrant, but in the deepest part of woods, where a tribe of cannibal dwarves lives, the girl is waiting for her time to come.

description: ACTION CAT to the rescue as a Fiery Meteorite plummets to earth! But more importantly...Beautiful Downtown Skokie!!! All seems normal except...what's wrong with Shelly? ALSO! The Villains of Action Cat become...HEROES? That's right! The BAD guys become GOOD guys! What's going on?! Join us for awesomeness featuring Action Cat aka Adorable Cat! Shelly! Hammond! Awesome Bear! Zombies! Pirates! And...Uncle Steve? From the famous cartoonists who brought you Tiny Titans and Itty Bitty HELLBOY!

Cinderella's search for answers about the rodent/mundy hybrids takes her across the globe! How do these "mice men" tie into Cindy's past? What is their endgame? And will Cindy figure things out before disaster falls on Fabletown? All this and a shocking appearance by...oh, well that would be telling!

Note: The digital edition (12/31/2013) of this issue was released a week before the print edition (1/8/2014).
name: Of Men and Mice, Part Two: Memories

description:
PAINKILLER JANE is on a manhunt. The bloody showdown take place in Rockaway, Queens as Jane confronts the man who kidnapped the princess. Meanwhile, father and son strike a dealwith the mysterious government bounty hunter named Churchill, as the princess and her protector go on the run, lost in America.

Note: The digital edition (12/31/2013) of this issue was released a week before the print edition (1/8/2014).
